[Pabna is the district to the immediate south of Sirajganj of the
previous report of 20 Aug 2010, and bordering the south bank of the
Sirajganj river. To find Pabna, go to
<http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pabna> and
<http://www.bengaliwiki.com/page/Pabna>. - Mod.MHJ]

[The HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Bangladesh is available
at <http://healthmap.org/r/03p3>. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
